Azure DDoS Protection protects Azure resources from Distributed Denial-of-Service attacks.

Features:

* Traffic monitoring
* Automatic mitigation
* Adaptive tuning
* Attack analytics

For example, an online retail website may experience a traffic flood attack during a major sale.

A real-life use case is e-commerce resilience.

Another example is financial services protecting customer portals.

Azure DDoS Protection preserves availability under malicious traffic conditions.
